These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
City: boston, colone, venice, liverpool
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. the person driving the airplane is the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching satire movies and the person traveling to boston##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| City         | liverpool      | boston | colone | venice |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | drama   | satire    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, water, mirinda
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Beverage   | water     | fanta | mirinda  | soy-milk |
| Transport     | taxi        | jet-ski  | boat    | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, accountant, dressmaker, project-manager
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the german is between the architect and the project-manager##2
2. the argentine is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the dressmaker##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the project-manager##1
5. the project-manager is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the accountant and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job          | architect | accountant   | project-manager     | dressmaker     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, yellow, orange, ebony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the person who likes ebony is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person who likes ebony is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the person who likes orange is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Color   | orange  | ebony      | fuchsia        | yellow     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, colombian, japanese
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, adventure, horror, time-travel
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the japanese is the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the colombian is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the person watching musical movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | american   | japanese   | colombian | canadian |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure      | time-travel | musical      | horror |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

