.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, cricket, baseball, rowing
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, sudoku, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Sport    | baseball   | rowing      | cricket       | water-polo |
| Hobby   | camping | woodworking | sudoku     | fishing |
| Pet     | rat     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla | hamster |

