.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, singing, baking, traveling
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, russian
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the russian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the russian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| Hobby           | traveling | singing | video-games   | baking |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | dutch     | russian     | italian |

