.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, satire, superhero
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, gardening, card-games, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | family      | mystery | satire |
| Hobby           | card-games   | gardening  | writing     | filmmaking |

