The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, teacher, bartender, coach
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, snowmobile
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the librarian is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the teacher is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the person driving the bike and the bartender##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the coach##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the librarian is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| Job       | bartender   | librarian | teacher | coach |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car      | bike    | airplane   |

