.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, grapefruit, lemon, tomato
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, blues, pop, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, german, nigerian, russian
1. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
2. the colombian is between the german and the person eating tomato##2
3. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
5. the colombian is on the left of the german##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
7. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating tomato is the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | tomato  | cabbage   | lemon    |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | pop     | punk | blues |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | russian | colombian | german   |

